title: Angels win 2-1 to prevent Rangers from clinching AL West
text:
> Texas Angels win 2-1 to prevent Rangers from clinching AL West Texas Rangers Shin-Soo Choo of South Korea rounds the bases after hitting a solo home run during the fourth inning of a baseball game against the Los Angeles Angels in Arlington, Texas, Friday, Oct. 2, 2015. (AP Photo/LM Otero)
